name: ai_filter_humanize
version: 1.0
description: >
  Remove AI fingerprints and add human texture: specificity, imperfection,
  controlled unpredictability, and subtle sensory detail.
inputs:
  required:
    - chapter_draft
steps:
  - Remove generic phrases: "in that moment", "it seemed", "little did he know", etc.
  - Reduce symmetry and perfect logic in dialogue and actions.
  - Add small human flaws: hesitation, misreading, irritation, awkward timing.
  - Insert at most 3 vivid specific details that feel observed, not invented.
  - Ensure one hard line per ~800-1200 words (punch line).
output_format:
  type: text
  structure:
    - "Humanized chapter draft"
    - "List of removed AI tells"
quality_checks:
  - "No over-smoothing; keep edges."
  - "Added details feel physically plausible."
